      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in impeccable condition. This example features the celebrated S54 3.2L inline-six, recently serviced with a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement for absolute mechanical peace of mind. The chassis is structurally perfect, having undergone preventative subframe reinforcement. Power is managed through a precise six-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, ensuring the 333hp reaches the tarmac with surgical accuracy. The factory finish exhibits incredible depth with no paint correction required, and the interior bolsters remain firm and free of wear. A turn-key specimen for the technical purist.",
